Class Customer

java.lang.Object
  Customer
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class Customer
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

The class Customer represents the customers of a bank. It has all the necessary fields such as firstName , lastName,etc that holds the first name and last name respectively. It also has all the methods required to manipulate all the fields
